<p><img class="alignnone size-large wp-image-870" src="http://virtualmoney-investment.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/z000010-1024x301.png" sizes="(max-width: 580px) 100vw, 580px" srcset="http://virtualmoney-investment.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/z000010-1024x301.png 1024w, http://virtualmoney-investment.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/z000010-300x88.png 300w, http://virtualmoney-investment.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/z000010-768x226.png 768w, http://virtualmoney-investment.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/z000010.png 1130w" alt="bitflyer取引高" width="580" height="170" /></p>
